list.abstract: program（英 [ˈprəʊɡræm]，美 [ˈproʊɡræm]），英语单词，作名词用，为节目；计划；节目单。作动词用，为设计程序；为…编制程序；安排。短语搭配有TV program（电视节目），例句为“Help their children understand the program's plot.（帮助他们的孩子理解节目的情节。）” program名词类近义词有procedure、routine、plan等。

yingyinNormal.en: So stick to the program, soldier!
yingyinNormal.zh: 遵守程序士兵!

yingyinNormal.en: The program terminal from an ICBM missile...
yingyinNormal.zh: 洲际导弹程序终端...

yingyinNormal.en: Tell me, what happened to your program?
yingyinNormal.zh: 告诉我，你的程序出了什么问题？

yingyinNormal.en: Why are these images in the program? Ender. We won.
yingyinNormal.zh: 程序里为什么会有这些图像？安德，我们赢了。

yingyinNormal.en: I don't understand. You built this program. Why is it trying to kill us?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不明白，是你设计的这个程序，可它为何要杀死我们？

yingyinNormal.en: Now, I meant to tell you, the Smart Blood program is obviously still in its developmental phase.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我想告诉你，智能血液程序很显然还在研发阶段。

yingyinNormal.en: If you do, my program will fail. This could be a real weapon. It's worth risking my life.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果你动手，我的程序就会失败，这是真正的武器，值得我拿生命冒险。

yingyinNormal.en: This guy invented Moss 865. Every office in the world uses that program. We use it. There you go.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他发明了摩斯865，全世界的公司都在用这个程序。我们也在用。你看吧。

yingyinNormal.en: I want to apply this to the Ultron program, but Jarvis can't download a data schematic this dense.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我想把这个用到奥创程序上，但是贾维斯下载不了密度这么大的数据原理图。

yingyinNormal.en: The program wasn't designed to alter the past. It was designed to affect the future. And you've done that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个程序的初衷不是为了改变过去而是左右未来，这你已经做到了这点。

yingyinNormal.en: It's a computer program, Captain. The girl on the train, all the others, they're lost. I am sorry about that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是电脑程序，上尉，车上的姑娘还有其他人，都已经死了，我很抱歉。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, Stuart. You want to mine some Bitcoin with us? We'll write the program, you bring the snacks? Too rich for my blood.
yingyinNormal.zh: 斯图尔特。你想跟我们一起挖比特币吗？我们写程序，你带零食？太高档穷人玩不起。

yingyinNormal.en: So let me get this straight. We have to write an elaborate program in order to find a fake coin that we can't spend on anything? Yes. That sounds fun.
yingyinNormal.zh: 让我理理。所以我们得精心写个程序来挖出我们花不了的假货币吗？是的。听起来真"有趣"啊。

yingyinNormal.en: Perhaps. Perhaps. Or perhaps the moment I do so, a program in that drive will seek out every device my laptop's been connected to, everyone that's close to me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 或许，或许，又或许我一插，盘里的程序马上就会搜索到我电脑联系过的所有装置，与我亲近的所有人。

yingyinNormal.en: So I'm gonna stand out in my program.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以我会开始接受培训。

yingyinNormal.en: Maybe we get through this program normal.
yingyinNormal.zh: 也许我们能像正常人一样完成实习。

yingyinNormal.en: I don't even know if I believe in your program.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我都不知道自己相不相信你的计划，

yingyinNormal.en: That's an experimental program Sir. Strictly off the books.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这计划还是实验阶段，而且流程不合规矩。

yingyinNormal.en: The Sentinel program was originally conceived by Dr. Bolivar Trask.
yingyinNormal.zh: 哨兵计划最初是玻利瓦尔特斯拉克博士提出的。

yingyinNormal.en: In fact, your acquisition by this program as well as the program itself has been reviewed and sanctioned by a military court.
yingyinNormal.zh: 实际上，你大脑的使用权和整个项目都通过了军事法庭的审核。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: "We see that the <highlight>program</highlight> is associated with a 30 percent reduction in deforestation," Ferraro says.
examination_example.sentence_trans: Ferraro说:“我们看到，该项目与减少30%的森林砍伐有关。”

examination_example.sentence: It takes about three weeks to a month to notice significant changes in your weight due to altering your training <highlight>program</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 大约需要三周到一个月的时间来注意到由于改变训练计划而导致的体重的显著变化。

examination_example.sentence: Now, a new Web-based company has developed the first "brain training <highlight>program</highlight>" designed to actually help people improve and regain their mental sharpness.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 现在，一家基于网络的新公司开发了第一个“大脑训练项目”，旨在帮助人们提高和恢复他们的思维敏捷度。

examination_example.sentence: The zoology <highlight>program</highlight> attracts students for whom zoo visits were the crucial formative experience that led them to major in biological sciences.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这个动物学课程吸引了许多学生，对他们来说，参观动物园是一段至关重要的成长经历，促使他们主修生物科学。

examination_example.sentence: The goal of grade forgiveness is less about the grade itself and more about encouraging students to retake courses critical to their degree <highlight>program</highlight> and graduation.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 分数减免的目的不是为了分数本身，而是为了鼓励学生重修对他们的学位课程和毕业至关重要的课程。

examination_example.sentence: The Web-based <highlight>program</highlight> allows you to systematically improve your memory and attention skills.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这个基于网络的课程可以系统地提高你的记忆力和注意力。

examination_example.sentence: The <highlight>program</highlight> keeps track of your progress and provides detailed feedback on your performance and improvement.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这个程序会跟踪你的进度，提供详细的反馈并改进性能。

examination_example.sentence: Rob McKinney, head of the International Road Assessment <highlight>Program</highlight>, says that all countries tend to go through three phases.

direction_info.description:
数据源自2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: In China, an international communication <highlight>program</highlight> was started to send support to other countries.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在中国，一个国际交流项目开始向其他国家提供支持。

examination_example.sentence: I'm having a great time on my student exchange <highlight>program</highlight> here.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我在这儿的学生交换项目过得很愉快。

examination_example.sentence: In China, Spring Bud Education <highlight>Program</highlight> (春蕾计划) has helped over 3 million girls go back to school.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在中国，春蕾计划已经帮助300多万女孩重返校园。

examination_example.sentence: One day after watching a science <highlight>program</highlight>, a little boy decided to dig a hole behind his house.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一天，一个小男孩在看完一个科学节目之后，决定在他的房子后面挖一个洞。

examination_example.sentence: The <highlight>program</highlight>, Everlasting Classics, encourages us to read more classics.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 节目《经典咏流传》鼓励我们多读经典作品。

examination_example.sentence: She appeared on television <highlight>programs</highlight> and in newspapers and magazines all over the world.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 她出现在世界各地的电视节目、报纸和杂志上。

examination_example.sentence: He is designed to teach a special <highlight>program</highlight> about environmental-friendly power created by the sun and wind.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他旨在教授一门关于由太阳能和风能创造的环保能源的特别课程。

examination_example.sentence: This <highlight>program</highlight>, started in 2005, used to be taught by human teachers.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这门课程始于2005年，过去由人类教师教授。

examination_example.sentence: The robot will have to have a certain way to receive the <highlight>program</highlight> so that it knows what it is to do.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 机器人必须有一个特定的方式来接收程序，这样它就知道它要做什么。

examination_example.sentence: More importantly, even the smartest computer <highlight>programs</highlight> can't guess and react to all the unexpected situations that educators face daily.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 更重要的是，即使是最智能的计算机程序也无法猜测和应对教育者每天面临的所有意想不到的情况。

examination_example.sentence: More importantly, it allows the <highlight>program</highlight> developers to improve Bill's behavior and knowledge base when needed.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 更重要地是，它允许程序开发人员在需要时改进比尔的行为和知识库。
